cu.explanation_en: Setting the DRB ciphering option to an unknown enum 'maybe' will cause configuration validation errors and prevent proper security setup for data radio bearers.

du.explanation_en: Setting the RF simulator model name to an unknown enum 'INVALID_MODEL' will cause initialization failures in the radio frequency simulation component.
du.explanation_zh: 將射頻模擬器模型名稱設定為未知的枚舉值 'INVALID_MODEL'，會導致射頻模擬組件初始化失敗。
